sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard / API)
    participant EvalHub as eval-hub API<br/>8080/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant InitContainer as eval-runtime-init<br/>(Init Container)
    participant S3 as S3 Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Adapter as Evaluation Adapter<br/>(Lighteval / lm-eval / etc.)
    participant Sidecar as eval-runtime-sidecar<br/>8080/TCP localhost
    participant MLflow as MLflow Tracking<br/>HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,OCI: Flow 1: Evaluation Job Creation & Execution

    Client->>EvalHub: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s)
    activate EvalHub

    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: TokenReview Response (authenticated user)

    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>trustyai.opendatahub.io/evaluations:create
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: SAR Response (allowed/denied)

    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap<br/>(job.json + sidecar_config.json)
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: ConfigMap created

    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: Create Batch Job<br/>(init + sidecar + adapter containers)
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: Job created

    EvalHub-->>Client: 201 Created (job_id)
    deactivate EvalHub

    Note over InitContainer,S3: Job Pod Startup Phase

    rect rgb(255, 248, 230)
        InitContainer->>S3: Download test data<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
        S3-->>InitContainer: Test data files
        Note over InitContainer: Init complete, adapter starts
    end

    Note over Adapter,OCI: Evaluation Execution Phase

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Adapter->>Sidecar: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}/events<br/>HTTP localhost:8080 (plaintext, pod-local)
        activate Sidecar
        Sidecar->>EvalHub: Forward request<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token injected<br/>TLS 1.2+
        EvalHub-->>Sidecar: Response
        Sidecar-->>Adapter: Response
        deactivate Sidecar

        Adapter->>Sidecar: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>HTTP localhost:8080
        activate Sidecar
        Sidecar->>MLflow: Forward request<br/>Auth: Projected SA Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
        MLflow-->>Sidecar: Run created
        Sidecar-->>Adapter: Response
        deactivate Sidecar

        Adapter->>Sidecar: PUT /v2/{repo}/blobs/uploads<br/>HTTP localhost:8080
        activate Sidecar
        Sidecar->>OCI: Forward request<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (challenge-response)<br/>TLS 1.2+
        OCI-->>Sidecar: Upload complete
        Sidecar-->>Adapter: Response
        deactivate Sidecar
    end

    Note over Client,EvalHub: Flow 2: Authentication & Authorization Detail

    Client->>EvalHub: GET /api/v1/evaluations/jobs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    activate EvalHub
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: TokenReview (cached 2min)
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: User identity
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: SAR (allow cache 5min, deny cache 30s)<br/>Namespace from X-Tenant header
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: Authorized
    EvalHub-->>Client: 200 OK (job list)
    deactivate EvalHub
